OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FPatients in A&E are at risk of getting
OL,7,Fworse because of missed doses of
OL,8,Fprescription medicines, according to a
OL,9,Fnew report.
OL,11,FThe study, from the Royal College of
OL,12,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM), found
OL,13,Fpeople in A&E were not getting their
OL,14,Fmedications on time and were missing
OL,15,Fdoses needed to manage their illnesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
