OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FTime critical medicines (TCM) are
OL,7,Fthose prescribed to a patient for
OL,8,Fexisting conditions, such as insulin
OL,9,Ffor diabetes, Parkinson's drugs,
OL,10,Fepilepsy medicines and tablets for
OL,11,Fpreventing blood clots.
OL,13,FIf these drugs are delayed or missed,
OL,14,Fthe patient can deteriorate and is at
OL,15,Fgreater risk of complications or death.
OL,17,FWhile patients are advised to remember
OL,18,Fto bring their medications to A&E and
OL,19,Fto take them, there is also a
OL,20,Fresponsibility on NHS staff to make
OL,21,Fsure this happens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
