OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FDespite the recognised risk of harm,
OL,7,Fthe delivery of TCM is not consistent
OL,8,Facross emergency departments, the RCEM
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FAnd some of the issues are made worse
OL,12,Fby long waiting times to be seen in
OL,13,FA&E.
OL,15,FIts new study focused on oral levodopa
OL,16,Ffor Parkinson's and insulin for
OL,17,Fdiabetes, as these are common in
OL,18,Fpatients in A&E and must be given on
OL,19,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
