OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FThe research is part of the College's
OL,7,Fclinical Quality Improvement Programme
OL,8,F(QIP) which aims to improve the care
OL,9,Fof A&E patients.
OL,11,FAcross the UK, 136 emergency
OL,12,Fdepartments submitted data for more
OL,13,Fthan 13,000 people in A&E who were on
OL,14,Finsulin injections or levodopa.
OL,16,FThe findings showed that more than
OL,17,Fhalf of these patients were not
OL,18,Fidentified as being on TCM within 30
OL,19,Fminutes of their arrival in an
OL,20,Femergency department.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
