OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FIn addition, 68% of doses were not
OL,7,Fadministered within 30 minutes of the
OL,8,Fexpected time.
OL,10,FDr Jonny Acheson, an emergency
OL,11,Fmedicine consultant in Leicester who
OL,12,Fhas Parkinson's, led the study. He
OL,13,Fsaid there has been improvements but
OL,14,Fmore needs to be done.
OL,16,F"The findings contained in this report
OL,17,Fshould serve as a call to action for
OL,18,Fboth emergency medicine staff, as well
OL,19,Fas patients reliant on time critical
OL,20,Fmedications, to ensure no dose is ever
OL,21,Fmissed in A&E," he said.
