OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,F"Everyone has a role to play `
OL,7,Fparamedics and emergency medicine
OL,8,Fstaff need to ask patients what
OL,9,Fmedications they take, and likewise,
OL,10,Fpeople with Parkinson's and insulin
OL,11,Ftreated diabetes need to tell staff
OL,12,Fthey take a TCM and take their meds
OL,13,Fwith them if they have to visit an A&E.
OL,15,F"We are pleased that focusing on
OL,16,Fidentifying these patients has led to
OL,17,Fimprovement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
