OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,F"However, the NHS must think about how
OL,7,Fthey identify people taking these
OL,8,Ftypes of medication and how they are
OL,9,Fable to ensure they receive their
OL,10,Fdoses on time, every time while they
OL,11,Fare in the emergency department.
OL,13,F"These medicines are critical to the
OL,14,Fquality of these patients lives and we
OL,15,Fhave a duty of care to ensure that
OL,16,Fthey receive them when they should."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
