OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FThe QIP team made recommendations,
OL,7,Fincluding that patients on TCM need to
OL,8,Fbe identified early when they attend
OL,9,FA&E to start the process of getting
OL,10,Fall doses.
OL,12,FSystems also need to be in place to
OL,13,Fensure timely administration of TCM,
OL,14,Fincluding self-administration, and
OL,15,Fthere should be a clear line of
OL,16,Fresponsibility for staff.
OL,18,FRCEM president-elect, Dr Ian
OL,19,FHigginson, welcomed the work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
