OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FHe added: "This is an example of a
OL,7,Fproblem we should not be having to fix
OL,8,Fin our emergency departments.
OL,10,F"It has risen to prominence because of
OL,11,Fthe increasing number of our patients
OL,12,Fwho are having to endure ridiculously
OL,13,Flong waits in our emergency
OL,14,Fdepartments ` 12, 24, 48 hours and
OL,15,Feven longer.
OL,17,F"It is vital that ensuring patients
OL,18,Freceive TCM is identified as an issue
OL,19,Fassociated with these waits.
