OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,F"Missing doses of medication for
OL,7,Fillnesses such as Parkinson's or
OL,8,Fdiabetes is not just inconvenient, it
OL,9,Fis dangerous; and missing multiple
OL,10,Fdoses can have serious consequences.
OL,12,F"This first-year report reveals there
OL,13,Fis already some good work happening
OL,14,Facross the country.
OL,16,F"Now we just need to ensure that it is
OL,17,Freplicated in every emergency
OL,18,Fdepartment and becomes embedded so
OL,19,Fthat no one fears not being able to
OL,20,Faccess their medication while in our
OL,21,Fcare."
