OL,3,CPatients in A&E 'risk getting worse
OL,4,Cbecause of missed medicine doses'
OL,6,FParkinson's UK, praised the RCEM's
OL,7,Fwork while Diabetes UK said delayed or
OL,8,Fmissed insulin doses can be a
OL,9,Fpotentially life-threatening emergency.
OL,11,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "We welcome
OL,12,Fthis report and will look closely at
OL,13,Fthe findings, to ensure any patient in
OL,14,Fneed of time critical medicine does
OL,15,Fnot lose out when in A&E and receives
OL,16,Fthe medication they need or support to
OL,17,Fself-administer as they would at home.
