OL,6,F"As the report makes clear, it is
OL,7,Fwelcome to see improvements thanks to
OL,8,Fthe hard work of frontline staff but
OL,9,Fmore generally we know A&E waiting
OL,10,Ftimes are far too long and our
OL,11,Fupcoming urgent and emergency care
OL,12,Fplan will set out how we aim to bring
OL,13,Fthese down ahead of next winter."
